Playtesting Rules



# PLAYTESTING RULES

- **Follow Main Rules**, Just Because You Are A Playtester, Doesnt Mean You Dont Follow The Main Rules, The Rules Apply To Everybody.

- **Listen To Staff**, Always Listen To Staff And Do As They Say, If You Repeatitively Blank Staff Commands, You Will Be Demoted From Playtester.

- **No Spoilers**, If You Post Any Leaks Or Spoilers For The Other Members In Chat Or DM's, You Will Have Your Playtester Role Removed.

- **Seek For Bugs**, It Is Your Job As A Playtester To Search For Bugs And Errors And Report Them To Staff.

- **Stay Active**, If You Are Absent From At Least 5 Playtesting Sessions, Your Role Will Be Removed.



