Creator Rules



# EXODUS OG CREATOR RULES

- **No Botting**, If Any Of Your Exodus OG Promotion Videos Are Not Official Or AI Generated, You Will Be Demoted From The Creator Role.

- **Must Include Link**, All Videos Must Include A Clear And Visible Link To Our Discord Server.

- **Must State We Are Not With Epic**, All Videos Must State That Exodus OG is NOT Afflicated With Epic Games.

- **Official Gameplay**, All Gameplay Shown In Your Video Must Be Gameplay From Exodus OG, Using Any Other Private Server For This Purpose Is Prohibited.

- **No Racism**, Your Exodus OG Promotion Videos Must NOT Include Any Racism, Phobia Or NSFW.



Creator Giveaways



# CREATOR GIVEAWAYS

**How Does It Work?**

Each Week, At Least One Promotion Video Gets Picked Out And Published On All Of Exodus OG's Social Pages, To Earn A Creator Giveaway Your Video Must Hold The Most Views Out Of All Of The Videos In That Week.

**Rewards**

10,000 Vbucks

Your Video Being Promoted In #creator-videos, And On All Of Exodus OG's Socials.



