Staff Rules



# EXODUS OG STAFF RULES

- **Respect Members**, Just Because You Are Staff, Doesn't Mean You Can Disrespect People.

- **No Leaking**, Sharing Any Unreleased Builds Or Game Leaks Will Result In You Being Demoted.

- **Handle Rule Breakers Correctly**, If You Are In The Situation Where You Need To Ban Someone, Make Sure To Inspect #punishments To Give The User The Correct Punishment.

- **No Role Abuse**, Please Do Not Abuse Your Role By Muting And Banning Members.

- **Player Reports**, Please Do Not Ban Members Without Evidence From A Proven Player Report.

- **No Favoritism**, Treat All Members The Same And Apply The Correct Punishment If Needed, Even If They're Your Friend.

- **Resignation**, If You Wish To Resign From Exodus OG, You Must Contact The Server Owner. Do Not Get Up And Walk Out.



Staff Announcements



# NEW UPDATE

**Due To The New Exodus OG Update, Some Users Might Experience Errors And Bugs More Frequently Than Usual. It Is Your Job To Assist Users Who Seek For Help Whether It's In A Chat Channel, Or A Support Ticket.

We Request All Staff And Admins To Answer All Tickets As Soon As Possible Within The Next Week. If You Are Unable To Do So, Please Leave A Message. Thank You.

||@Admin||



Punishments


# EXODUS OG PUNISHMENTS

**NOTE: Please Only Use The Correct Punishment For The Right Rule.**

- Racism: Permanently Banned
- Phobia: Permanently Bannned
- NSFW: Permanently Banned
- Cheating: Backend Ban
- Spamming: Mute 1h, Mute 1w, Mute Perm
- Ban Evading: Permanently Banned | Reported To Discord TOS
- Teaming: Backend Ban (Appealable)
- Pinging Admins: Mute 1w, Mute Perm
- Self Promotion: Mute Perm
- False Reporting: 1w Ban
- Stream Sniping: 30 Day Ban
- Doxxing: Permanently Banned



